            <lg xml:id="TK483">
<l>aruviṉai yeṉpa vuḷavō karuviyāṟ</l>
<l>kāla maṟintu ceyiṉa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is there anything difficult for him to do, who acts, with (the right) instruments at the right time ?</l>
